description: From the Lakehaven shops the walk follows the bikepath around Lake Budgewoi and closes the loop through Toukley and Gorokan.

markers.description: Get the train to Wyong and the connecting bus to Lake Haven using transportnsw.info.
From the bus stops follow the footpath past the cinema.
Follow Kanimbla Ave from the carpark behind the cinema.
At the end of Kanimbla Ave, turn right down Moala Parade.
At the intersection follow Panorama Ave to the left.
From the dog park at the end follow Lowana Ave left to the Pacific Highway.
Follow the bike path along the Pacific Highway to the right to the bridge.
Cross the bridge and take the ramp right, down to the riverside.
Follow the shared path along the lake.
Cross the bridge over the canal and continue down the shared path.
Don't miss the turn right at Edgewater Park.
From Edgewater Park follow the shared park along the lake.
Take the ramp up to the bridge and cross Budgewoi Creek.
From Slade park on the other side of the bridge follow the bike path along the sports fields.
After the roundabout follow the Darren Smith Memorial Cycleway along the Central Coast Highway.
Across the highway from Lakes Beach Surf club follow Werepi Street through a bushland area.
On the far side turn right and follow the footpath along the Central Coast Highway.
At the roundabout, cross Main Road and continue along the Central Coast Highway.
Follow the footpath through the reserve and continue down Ocean Parade.
Cross Evans Road and continue down the footpath between the houses to a dog park.
Exit the dog park to the right down Mongomery Ave.
From the intersection follow Belbowrie Street left to Canton Beach.
Follow the footpath along Canton Beach to the right.
Past the sailing club, follow the footpath along Moss Avenue to Main Road.
Follow Main road to the left to the Toukley Bridge.
Cross the bridge and take the ramp to the left underneath the bridge.
Cross Wallarah Point Peace Park to The Corso.
Follow the footpath along The Corso to the right.
At the intersection with Goobarabah Ave turn left.
Follow Goobarabah Ave past the school to the carpark of Lake Haven.
Cross the carpark to the bus stops.
Get the bus back from Lake Haven using transportnsw.info.
